     <S id="S1">
          <FORM>k'anna ka kava'angs-en ti Jesus: ni-K'ma ti Petrus-an, Meirangta ti atta. Irou kamillingigh ta ti-Si-mon Petrus ka Meirangta ti atta, ni æht-tin tyn ta pa-haalap-pen tynmammia, ('alei kKa mananata teni) kani-pou-raloum tyni-an pou-vaoung.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S3">
          <FORM>8 Ka Pahtatæutau-han ka ra-rouma ni-ierroua Jam ki avang (nda assi madallia neini-æn ta pourough rouha lava kæætoug-han kina rarpung ki pariou) ka vihit-ten nein ta sasamlid ka yd-dad-'ing-en.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S5">
          <FORM>9 Irou ka ni-mou-pourough ta neni, ni-kytt'an nein ta ni-at-ta-kou-'an ki apoei ka væ', ka pakah-halap-pan ki't' hungh ki pasul.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S7">
          <FORM>10 Ni-k'ma ta tiJesus neini-æn,'Ad-dei ki 't' hungh k'anna ka ni-'ara-oumi hnyn.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S9">
          <FORM>11 Ka ni-mou-vavau ta tiSimon Petrus vihit ki sa-samlid pou-pourough kamatmoei ki 't' hung ka irirang sat kæ'ætoug - han 'æb ki rymma kytti-æn 'æb ki tou-ro: moukouna ka dagh ka kma-hynna, ashi ni-'k-hyt ta sa-samlid.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S11">
          <FORM>12 Ni-k'ma ta ti Jesus neini-æn, Mou-kouw'-appa hia, mi-ran-ga-ranga mavok. Ka mangala ta ti-mamang ki Pahta-tutæu-hantmaligh tyni-æn, Ti mang kow?</FORM>
     </S>
